data.description: WOW! Seller is offering a $5000 credit with an acceptable offer! This is a Fabulous location within Captain's Cove. On a secluded cul-de-sac, you will find this adorable 3 br/2 full bath home. Home features great open floor plan with vaulted ceiling in the living, dining and 2 of the bedrooms. There are brand-new Stainless-Steel Samsung appliances, fresh paint, new luxury vinyl plank flooring and new HVAC outside unit and air handler. Attached garage is finished with a work space and cabinets.
